cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving wireless network performance.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper extensively discusses the use of machine learning techniques.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses optimizing communication parameters to improve QoS and QoE.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of data-driven approaches and machine learning.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still relevant as the paper discusses optimizing network performance through control of communication parameters.
